========================================================================================

Conversation locker plugin for Pidgin v1.0 (10/02/09)

Please refer to online documentation at http://pidgin-conversation-locker.googlecode.com

========================================================================================



Installation
--------------------------------------------------------------

1. From terminal cd to the directory containing extracted plugin archieve.

2. If you wish to install plugin for all users (system wide), enter into terminal

	sudo bash install.sh

   and then when asked for the choice, "1".

 (Optional) if  you wish to install plugin for only current user, enter into terminal

 	sudo install.sh

   and then when asked for the choice, "2".

 3. Restart Pidgin if it is already running. Enable plugin from Tools -> Plugins interface.

